data.description:
This unique and sprawling ranch home is situated on 1.46 acres of park-like wooded grounds. The property features a large eat-in kitchen with an abundance of cabinets and counter space. The living room is spacious and inviting, with a fireplace and a large bay window that lets in plenty of natural light. The home also has a formal dining room, a family room, and a sunroom.
 
The home features all hard wood doors, several ceilings made of cherry wood and the unique office/4th bedroom has a burlap ceiling and wormy chestnut walls.

The bedrooms are all generously sized, and the master bedroom has a feature wall and ceiling that is made of cherry hard wood. 

The large patio area is perfect for outdoor entertaining.

The property is located in a quiet and peaceful neighborhood, just minutes from schools, shopping, and restaurants. It is also close to several parks and recreation areas
